    <description>Line Items that constitute the invoice details
Payment Line Items represent individual entries associated with a payment transaction. Each line item provides detailed information about the specific amount applied to each invoice line on the applied invoice
Population Requirement Details: If triggers are ON, system will automatically create the payment lines on creation of the payment record. If triggers are turned OFF, then can be loaded manually. Individual allocation update - it has to be done at the payment line level. The amount on the payment line is to be less than or equal to the invoice line item.
[MODULE: Finance]
[LOAD: Optional]
[PREREQUISITES: Payments &amp; Credits (if loading with Triggers OFF)]
[REPLACEMENT OBJECT API: NA]
[COMMENTS: NA]</description>
